rows.label: qst202103_msg001
rows.name:
Whoa?! Yippee-ki-yay!
I got a response!

rows.label: qst202103_msg002
rows.name: That's the tablet mystery solved, then!

rows.label: qst202103_msg003
rows.name:
Ah, no, I don't think we can consider it
solved completely just yet.

rows.label: qst202103_msg005
rows.name:
Well, this stone tablet seems to be
indicating the World Tree.

rows.label: qst202103_msg008
rows.name:
After we unlocked the tablet,
that part lit up.

rows.label: qst202103_msg009
rows.name:
I think it's showing us the part of the
World Tree called the Data Processing
Room...

rows.label: qst202103_msg010
rows.name:
If we go there, something should be
waiting for us.

rows.label: qst202103_msg011
rows.name:
But there's no way to know
unless we actually go and check?

rows.label: qst202103_msg013
rows.name:
I have a duty to investigate
as soon as possible!

rows.label: qst202103_msg016
rows.name:
Yeah, but going alone to the
World Tree? That's a whole new
level of reckless!
